  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.10">
<l>neṭumā lavaṉmē viyanīr malaimēl nilavum pukaḻmaṅ kaiyarkō ṉamaril</l>
<l>kaṭamā kaḷiyā ṉaivallāṉ kaliya ṉolicey tamiḻmā laivallārk kuṭaṉē</l>
<l>viṭumāl viṉaivēṇ ṭiṭilmē lulaku meḷitā yiṭumaṉ ṟiyilaṅ kolicēr</l>
<l>koṭumā kaṭalvai yakamāṇ ṭumatik kuṭaimaṉ ṉavarā yaṭikū ṭuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master this garland of Tamil composed of the words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">the master in battle of huge elephants, rutting [with] musth,</l>
<l>The king of those of Maṅkai with far-reaching fame, about Nīrmalai</l>
<l rend="indent">where the tall, dark one dwells,</l>
<l>If [they] truly desire, their karma will certainly be dispatched immediately</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the upper world will surely become an easy thing.</l>
<l>Moreover, becoming kings with moon[-like] umbrellas, having ruled the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">[with] the glittering, roaring, swelling, wild, vast sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will join the feet [of the lord].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
